---
title: Creamy Spiced Chicken & Potato Mash with Garlicky Baby Broccoli & Asparagus
description: The star of tonight's meal is this homestyle sauce; velvety cream is gently infused with chicken stock to make a sauce that pairs perfectly with chicken and fluffy potato mash. You simply won’t believe you made this amazing meal at home!

